snippet.title: The First Descendant│Season 2 Void Chaser Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Season 2: Void Chaser launches December 5! Meet new Descendants, Keelan and Ultimate Sharen, with the loyal companion "Fellow" by your side. Conquer the fresh Void Vessel dungeon and take on the mighty boss, Dread Armor. 
Join the action—PLAY FREE NOW: tfd.nexon.com

The First Descendant is a next generation third-person co-op action RPG shooter (looter shooter) featuring high-quality graphics developed using Unreal Engine 5. It presents fun strategic boss fights through 4-player co-op, various unique characters, exciting gunplay, and looting.

⭐️Follow us and receive our latest news!⭐️
